data.description: Sanctuary in the heart of Omaha priced WAY under appraised value! This stunning home combines modern luxury with eco-friendly living, thanks to its solar panels (25 year warranty) that slash energy costs to nearly zero. Revel in the comfort of an updated kitchen and flooring, seamlessly blending style and functionality. The 4 seasons enclosed patio looks out to a fully fenced yard with storage shed. Nestled in a convenient neighborhood, enjoy access to shopping, dining and local community center complete with pool and park. Don't miss your chance to own this energy-efficient gem, where green living meets contemporary elegance. AMA
